      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING PFEIFFER (3) struggled for best form latest, finishing 5th (30.16) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won two of two tries. Has ability and can bounce back. IMPERATOR (2) was below best latest but did hit the frame in quick time two back when second (23.07) at this track in a Grade 5. Expected to do much better this time. NABIAC JACK (1) hit the ground running and was prominent to the turn but faded out of it when 6th at Taree Super Track in Grade 5 company. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Worth another chance. PATIENT VICKY (7) best form can see her take this out.",
